description:
Strictly Come Dancing Season 10 Episode 23 The Results

Tess Daly and Claudia Winkleman are your hosts for the Strictly semi-final results show. The drama is turned up full as the ballroom loses another couple in this eviction.
As well as a performance from the brilliant Katherine Jenkins, our professional couples take you to their very own Winter Wonderland for a beautiful group routine.
